      <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">GovWifi Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">The GovWifi service</h2>
      <p>
        GovWifi is a cross-government service that provides wifi access in government
        buildings. It’s managed centrally by Government Digital Service (GDS), which
        is part of the Cabinet Office. It’s set up and supported by host organisations
        which provide the service to one or more government organisations.
      </p>

