            the Civil Service Code and the social media guidance for civil servants.
          </li>
          <li>
            Your host organisation may:
            <ul class="list list-bullet">
              <li>restrict access for lawful purposes</li>
              <li>
                set their own acceptable use policies - contact your host
                organisation for more information on their policies
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            GDS will store your connection details, including your:
            <ul class="list list-bullet">
              <li>email address</li>
              <li>mobile telephone number</li>
              <li>authentication attempts</li>
              <li>activation and last login dates</li>
              <li>IP address</li>
